reviewText: Absolutely Love the Series and Excellent reproduction of the original Tapes.

i loved red shoe diaries and i've been looking for the episodes i watched and i love the story and the characters. i have not watched this dvd yet cause it just came yesterday. the episode i wanted for a long time and that is on this dvd is "gina"

Very sensual, the music is fantastic, a storyline that is equal to the title, as there are several.
I love the dancing and enjoy the diaries...
I am a David Duchovny fan and wish that he were in the movies as well as reading the narrative.
I have kept diaries for the last 25 years and that is what caught my attention, that being said, mine pale in comparison.
Looking at the gorgeous men is worth the watching and the ladies are pretty great as well, I happen to enjoy looking at a great looking man with a body to die for, but that's just me.
I love red shoe diaries movies! Fun adult entertainment! You never know what to expect... it is a complete and total release into a fantasy realm. LOVE IT
